_sText: There are two bases. both have three floors. first floor is the spawn area, and shotgus(both types). second floor is boat bording scouts and the launch button. look at the launch button and prees E to launch the boat. press it again while the boat is at its destination to make it return. To get insde the boat simpilt bump the wall blocking you. go inside the tube in the boat and swim up for a protected shooting point. Third floor dosen't have much yet, but will hold a rocket launcher in v2.
